#####################################################################
##                          PRESENTATION                           ##
#####################################################################

                          Charge Abe, discharge your brain, go party.

 *  Public install :    not yet
 *  Homepage:           http://rocknroot.org/content/abe
 *  Version :           0.1-Hilton - under development

  Abe is kind of a personnal encyclopedia where you can throw notes
and definitions and maybe organize them later.

  You can also sharedsome with friends, set them public and other
social stuff.

  Code is free, so if you're paranoid, you can install it at home or
in the little private internet of yours.

#####################################################################
##                            FEATURES                             ##
#####################################################################

Implemented:

Incoming:
 *  Categories: you can create categories (like folders) to put
    others categories or terms into.
 *  Terms: terms are definitions, write down your knowledge.
 *  Users: contents are linked with an user, you need one.
 *  categories/terms operations : move, copy
 *  tinyMCE integration
 *  different terms types
 *  some design things

